sec\/speed 6<b>."},{"content":"Serve sweet potato mash with baked fish."}],"hintsAndTricks":["A take on classic fish and chips. In this healthier alternative, delicate fish fillets are lightly coated in Parmesan breadcrumbs then baked until crisp and golden, while a creamy sweet potato mash is made in the Thermomix. Serve with green peas or a side salad.","Baking time will depend on the thickness of the fish fillets. Adjust time accordingly until fish is cooked."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}